::DrillBit::

He heard KitKat's orders. He would have liked to stay and teach the
Alliance a thing or too, but an order was an order.
"Predicons, fall back!" 
He started running to the location, KitKat had sent.

::Hot Rod::

He got the location.
"Be there in a few minutes, Magnus."
He took off for the mountin.
